  title: AR using Vuforia
  sections:
  - heading: Vuforia
    text: Vurforia provides AR functionality across several platforms, including
      Unity.
    linkText: Home Page
    url: https://developer.vuforia.com/home
  - heading: Documentation
    text: Documentation on how to use the different features of Vuforia can be found
      here, including image targets, plane tracking, model tracking, and more.
    linkText: Getting started in Unity
    url: https://developer.vuforia.com/library/vuforia-engine/getting-started/development-environments/getting-started-vuforia-engine-unity/
  - heading: Installation
    text: The package can be downloaded directly from the Vuforia site and added
      to a project, or it can be found on the Asset Store and linked that way.
